# Opulent-X Blockchain

**Opulent-X Blockchains** is a **realm** of Ethereum Layer 2 networks commissioned for robust **Inter-Chain Asset Management**(ICAM) ; **Internet of Everything** (IoE); and **Innovative Blockchain Integration** (BIT). Thus, helping you significantly to synergize your  Crypto Investment, Business Operation and Innovations respectively. 

- [ ] Ethereum Layer 2 (For Cross-Chain Features)
- [ ] Web3
- [ ] Internet of Everything (IoE)
- [ ] ISIC


## Opulent-X Gas Stations (Oxyn)

For you to be able to get opulented with this blockchain realm. You need to synergize your account (wallet) with Oxyn (OXY).  
OXY is the native token of this realm, which is primary use for paying gas fee (transaction fee) to service rendered by core validation engine.

You can get this Premier Crypto-Commodity at the following Gas Stations
- [ ] [Opulent-X Decentralized Gas Station (Eth needed)](www.opulent-x.com)
- [ ] [Opulent-X Swap Station](www.opulent-x.com) 
- [ ] [Opulent-X Airdrop Station(Free)](www.opulent-x.com)
- [ ] [Opulent-X Wallet (Free)](www.opulent-x.com)

_To pre-empt Pump-And-Dump Attack and to maintain stable crypto economic ecosystem, we pre-mined 100 Trillion Oxyns and securely store on our Military-Grade Secure Crypto Reserve Vaults(S-CRV)._

